RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Welcome to the Starsector combat tutorial. This part will go over the combat basics. Let's get started!"
constant: Welcome to the Starsector combat tutorial. This part will go over the combat basics.\n\nLet's get started!
constantCN: 欢迎来到 远行星号 作战教程。这一部分我们将熟悉各种基础战斗事项。\n\n让我们开始吧！

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Your flagship for this tutorial is a Hammerhead class destroyer. First things first - let's learn how to get it moving."
constant: Your flagship for this tutorial is a Hammerhead class destroyer. First things first - let's learn how to get it moving.
constantCN: 本教程中你的旗舰是一艘 锤头-级 驱逐舰。我们先来学习舰船操作中最基本的 - 移动。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "(By the way - you can pause and unpause the game at any time by pressing "
constant: (By the way - you can pause and unpause the game at any time by pressing

constantCN: 来在任何时候暂停游戏。)

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Press %s and %s to turn, %s and %s to accelerate forward or back, and hold %s to bring your ship to a halt. Give this a try, and press "Continue" when you've got the hang of it."
constant: Press %s and %s to turn, %s and %s to accelerate forward or back, and hold %s to bring your ship to a halt. Give this a try, and press "Continue" when you've got the hang of it.
constantCN: 按键盘 %s 和 %s 旋转转向，%s 和 %s 加速或反方向加速，和按 %s 把船停下来。您可以试操作一下，熟悉了后就点 "继续"。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Moving the mouse around pans your view. You can also use the mouse wheel to zoom in and out."
constant: Moving the mouse around pans your view. You can also use the mouse wheel to zoom in and out.
constantCN: 以鼠标左右移动改变视野位置，滚轮缩放视野。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Ships can also strafe sideways. This is particularly useful if you want to move while keeping your front-facing weapons pointed at your target."
constant: Ships can also strafe sideways.\n\nThis is particularly useful if you want to move while keeping your front-facing weapons pointed at your target.
constantCN: 舰船也可以直接横向平移。\n\n这项操作在您希望移动的同时保持前向武器指向目标时非常有用。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Your ship will turn towards your mouse pointer while you strafe, so keep the cursor on top of the target."
constant: Your ship will turn towards your mouse pointer while you strafe, so keep the cursor on top of the target.
constantCN: 您的舰船在平移时会将舰首转向鼠标指针，因此请把光标对准目标。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "There's now an enemy ship - an Enforcer-class destroyer - at your 12 o'clock. Its weapon and maneuvering systems are disabled."
constant: There's now an enemy ship - an Enforcer-class destroyer - at your 12 o'clock. Its weapon and maneuvering systems are disabled.
constantCN: 现在系统为您生成了一艘虚拟敌舰，它是一艘 执法者-级 驱逐舰，就在您正前方。别担心，它的动力和武装系统均已下线。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Let's try strafing - hold down %s and press %s or %s to circle around the enemy ship. You'll also need to use %s and %s to manage the distance. Continue when you feel comfortable with it."
constant: Let's try strafing - hold down %s and press %s or %s to circle around the enemy ship. You'll also need to use %s and %s to manage the distance.\n\nContinue when you feel comfortable with it.
constantCN: 让我们来试试平移 - 按住 %s 然后按 %s 或 %s 绕着敌舰周旋。您也需要按 %s 或 %s 维持恰当的距离。\n\n熟悉这项操作之后即可继续。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "The Hammerhead's weapons are organized in three groups. Press %s, %s, and %s to switch between groups, and %s to fire the selected group. Give this a try, and continue when you're ready."
constant: The Hammerhead's weapons are organized in three groups. Press %s, %s, and %s to switch between groups, and %s to fire the selected group.\n\nGive this a try, and continue when you're ready.
constantCN: 这艘 锤头-级 的武器被安置在三个武器组之中。按 %s{，}%s 与 %s 在不同的武器组之间切换，并按 %s 让选定的武器组开火。\n\n进行试射，并在您准备好进行下一步时继续。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Guided missiles require a target. By default, they'll lock on to the enemy nearest to your cursor when you fire."
constant: Guided missiles require a target. By default, they'll lock on to the enemy nearest to your cursor when you fire.
constantCN: 制导导弹会自动锁定一个目标。如果您不去为它们选目标的话，它们会自动锁定开火时离光标最近的敌人。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "You can also lock onto a specific enemy to ensure missiles go after it, and to see more information about it."
constant: You can also lock onto a specific enemy to ensure missiles go after it, and to see more information about it.
constantCN: 您还可以锁定一个特定的敌人，以确保导弹去追击它，同时，您也能查看锁定目标的详细信息。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Hover over the enemy ship and press %s to target it."
constant: Hover over the enemy ship and press %s to target it.
constantCN: 将光标停留在敌舰上并按 %s 就可以锁定它。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "You can press %s again to clear the target. Now, onto defenses - most ships use shields to defend against incoming damage."
constant: You can press %s again to clear the target.\n\nNow, onto defenses - most ships use shields to defend against incoming damage.
constantCN: 您可以再次按 %s 解除锁定。\n\n现在，关注防御方面 - 大多数舰船使用护盾抵御来袭的攻击。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "The Hammerhead has front-facing shields, but some ships have omni-directional shields that can rotate to face threats from any direction. %s to turn on your shields."
constant: The Hammerhead has front-facing shields, but some ships have omni-directional shields that can rotate to face threats from any direction.\n\n%s to turn on your shields.
constantCN: 锤头-级 拥有前向护盾，但有些舰船拥有全向护盾。全向护盾可以指向任意方向。\n\n%s 打开您的护盾。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Firing most weapons (except for missiles) generates flux. Your ship has a limited flux capacity, and managing what you use it on is key to survival. You can see your current flux level on the info display in the lower left corner of the screen."
constant: Firing most weapons (except for missiles) generates flux. Your ship has a limited flux capacity, and managing what you use it on is key to survival. You can see your current flux level on the info display in the lower left corner of the screen.
constantCN: 大多数武器 (除了导弹) 开火都会产生幅能。而舰船的幅能容量是有上限的，所以对幅能合适的管理决定了您在战场上的表现...以及性命。您可在屏幕左下角的舰船信息上悉知您目前的幅能容量。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Fire your Assault Chainguns (group 1) for a bit and watch how they build up flux, then continue when you're ready."
constant: Fire your Assault Chainguns (group 1) for a bit and watch how they build up flux, then continue when you're ready.
constantCN: 您可以试着用您的突击链炮 (1 号武器组) 发射几枚子弹，并仔细观察下它们是怎么产生幅能的，了解后点继续。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "The flux from firing these dissipates almost as quickly as it's generated. Different ships and ship loadouts dissipate flux at different rates, and so can support varying amounts of weapons effectively."
constant: The flux from firing these dissipates almost as quickly as it's generated. Different ships and ship loadouts dissipate flux at different rates, and so can support varying amounts of weapons effectively.
constantCN: 武器开火产生的幅能会很快被耗散。但不同舰船的幅能耗散速度是不同的，所以能支撑的武器数量也各不相同。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Shields generate flux continuously while they're up, and generate even more flux every time they absorb damage."
constant: Shields generate flux continuously while they're up, and generate even more flux every time they absorb damage.
constantCN: 护盾只要一开启就会持续产生幅能，且在吸收伤害时将会瞬间产生更多幅能。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "(So, even if you're not taking any damage on the shields, keeping them off will let you put out more firepower.)"
constant: (So, even if you're not taking any damage on the shields, keeping them off will let you put out more firepower.)
constantCN: (所以，在您未受到过多威胁时，保持护盾的关闭可以让您节省幅能，释放出更强大的火力。)

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Now, let's see how the shields hold up under fire."
constant: Now, let's see how the shields hold up under fire.
constantCN: 现在，让我们看看护盾是怎样承受炮火的。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "The enemy ship has stopped firing, but your flux level still isn't going down!"
constant: The enemy ship has stopped firing, but your flux level still isn't going down!
constantCN: 尽管敌舰已停止射击，但是您的幅能水平仍居高不下。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Flux gained when shields absorb damage is called hard flux and only dissipates while the shields are off - so, you can't keep shields up indefinitely while taking damage."
constant: Flux gained when shields absorb damage is called hard flux and only dissipates while the shields are off - so, you can't keep shields up indefinitely while taking damage.
constantCN: 护盾吸收伤害时产生的幅能是 '硬' 幅能，它只能在护盾关闭时才可耗散。所以一直挂着护盾妄想半无敌的梦就别做了。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Flux gained from firing weapons is called soft flux, and can dissipate while the shields are up."
constant: Flux gained from firing weapons is called soft flux, and can dissipate while the shields are up.
constantCN: 武器开火时产生的幅能是 '软' 幅能，而它能在护盾开启时耗散。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "The notch on the flux bar indicates your hard flux level."
constant: The notch on the flux bar indicates your hard flux level.
constantCN: 幅能条上的凸出方格代表了您当前的硬幅能水平。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - " to turn off your shields and let the flux dissipate."
constant: to turn off your shields and let the flux dissipate.
constantCN: 关闭您的护盾让幅能耗散。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Good. Now, let's see what happens if you keep your shields on under fire for too long."
constant: Good. Now, let's see what happens if you keep your shields on under fire for too long.
constantCN: 好。现在，让我们看看如果您的护盾在对方火力下保持太久会发生什么。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "%s to turn on your shields again and let the enemy keep firing at you."
constant: %s to turn on your shields again and let the enemy keep firing at you.
constantCN: %s 再次打开您的护盾，让敌人不断向您射击。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "As you can see, it's not good - when flux maxes out from shield hits, your ship overloads."
constant: As you can see, it's not good - when flux maxes out from shield hits, your ship overloads.
constantCN: 如您所见，当护盾吸收的伤害使幅能超过上限后，您的舰船将直接过载。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "While the ship is overloaded, it can't fire or raise shields, dissipates flux very slowly, but can still maneuver normally."
constant: While the ship is overloaded, it can't fire or raise shields, dissipates flux very slowly, but can still maneuver normally.
constantCN: 当舰船过载时，就无法射击或使用护盾了，而且只会以非常缓慢的速度耗散幅能，幸运的是，您仍然能控制其移动 (在脆弱的引擎还没被打爆的前提下)

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Wait for the overload to end."
constant: Wait for the overload to end.

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Now that the ship is no longer overloaded, flux is back to dissipating at a normal rate."
constant: Now that the ship is no longer overloaded, flux is back to dissipating at a normal rate.
constantCN: 现在舰船已经不再过载了，幅能耗散也恢复到正常水平。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "You can also vent flux to dissipate it at double the normal rate."
constant: You can also vent flux to dissipate it at double the normal rate.
constantCN: 您也可以主动排幅，以正常两倍的耗散速率来迅速排放幅能。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "While venting, your ship can't fire or use shields, so you generally only want to do it when it's safe."
constant: While venting, your ship can't fire or use shields, so you generally only want to do it when it's safe.
constantCN: 当您在主动排幅时，您的舰船是不能使用武器或护盾的，所以一般只有在安全情况下才会启用。且无法取消，只能等到结束。
那么现在按 %s 键来主动排幅。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Good. As you can see, you've now been flanked by a pair of Lasher-class frigates."
constant: Good. As you can see, you've now been flanked by a pair of Lasher-class frigates.
constantCN: 您看！您正被两艘 征伐-级 护卫舰夹击。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "They're going to start launching missiles at you. Fortunately, these missiles aren't very effective vs well-armored ships."
constant: They're going to start launching missiles at you. Fortunately, these missiles aren't very effective vs well-armored ships.
constantCN: 他们正在向您发射导弹。还好，这些导弹对您那精良的装甲没有多大效果。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Just sit tight and let them get a few volleys off."
constant: Just sit tight and let them get a few volleys off.
constantCN: 您大可以坐下来喝杯茶等它们几轮齐射完毕。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "It'd be nice to shoot these down - we've got some point-defense lasers just for that. But, it's almost impossible to manually target all the incoming missiles."
constant: It'd be nice to shoot these down - we've got some point-defense lasers just for that. But, it's almost impossible to manually target all the incoming missiles.
constantCN: 能拦截那些导弹就好了 - 而我们正好有防御激光。但是，要手动瞄准拦截那些导弹几乎是不可能的。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Fortunately, you can set any weapon group on autofire, making the weapons identify and attack targets on their own."
constant: Fortunately, you can set any weapon group on autofire, making the weapons identify and attack targets on their own.
constantCN: 幸运的是，还好您可以将任何武器组设置成自动开火模式，让它们自行索敌并攻击目标。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/super.createScript - String - "Press %s to enable autofire for the point-defense lasers in group 3. Make sure you have a different group selected - selecting an autofiring group will result in a manual override of its controls."
constant: Press %s to enable autofire for the point-defense lasers in group 3. Make sure you have a different group selected - selecting an autofiring group will result in a manual override of its controls.
constantCN: 按下 %s 让位于编组 3 的点防御激光进入自动开火模式，然后确保您选定了另一个武器编组。自动开火模式编组被选定时将强制进入手动控制模式。

constant: This jump-point has multiple possible destinations, and the gravimetric readings are too chaotic to provide any useful data.

constant: Gravimetric readings and nav data projections indicate there are no significant objects near this jump-point's destination.

constant: Gravimetric readings and nav data projections indicate significant objects near this jump-point's destination.

constant: Which mods this game was ever saved with, last saved with, and which mods are currently enabled.
constantCN: 曾保存过哪些 MOD，最后保存过哪些 MOD，以及当前启用了哪些 MOD。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/save/LoadGameDialogOld$3.createImpl - String - "This save is using a total conversion ("TC") mod that is no longer enabled. It is extremely unlikely to load properly until that mod is re-enabled."
constant: This save is using a total conversion ("TC") mod that is no longer enabled. It is extremely unlikely to load properly until that mod is re-enabled.
constantCN: 由于此存档所使用的独立 MOD 未被激活，在重新启用该 MOD 前，该存档将极有可能无法加载。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/save/LoadGameDialogOld$3.createImpl - String - "This save is using a normal mod that is no longer enabled. It is unlikely to load properly until that mod is re-enabled."
constant: This save is using a normal mod that is no longer enabled. It is unlikely to load properly until that mod is re-enabled.
constantCN: 由于此存档所使用的 普通 MOD 未被激活，在重新启用该 MOD 前，该存档将有可能无法加载。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/save/LoadGameDialogOld$3.createImpl - String - "This save is using a utility mod that is no longer enabled. However, it should work properly without that mod being enabled."
constant: This save is using a utility mod that is no longer enabled. However, it should work properly without that mod being enabled.
constantCN: 该存档一些 通用 功能性 Mod 未被激活，但是，即便不激活这些 Mod，该存档也能正常加载。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/save/LoadGameDialogOld$3.createImpl - String - "Starsector is running with a total conversion mod that is not used by this save. The save is extremely unlikely to load properly."
constant: Starsector is running with a total conversion mod that is not used by this save. The save is extremely unlikely to load properly.
constantCN: 由于 Starsector 正在使用该存档没启用的独立 MOD，该存档极有可能无法加载。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/save/LoadGameDialogOld$3.createImpl - String - "Starsector is running with mod(s) that are not used by this save. Depending on how the mod(s) are written, this may work properly or not at all."
constant: Starsector is running with mod(s) that are not used by this save. Depending on how the mod(s) are written, this may work properly or not at all.
constantCN: 该存档在保存时未激活上述 Mod。根据当前所加载的 Mod，该存档可能正常加载或根本无法使用。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/save/LoadGameDialogOld$3.createImpl - String - "This save is using a mod version that's a major mismatch from the one you have enabled. It is unlikely to load properly, or work once it's loaded with this version of the mod."
constant: This save is using a mod version that's a major mismatch from the one you have enabled. It is unlikely to load properly, or work once it's loaded with this version of the mod.
constantCN: 该存档中的 MOD 版本与你启用的版本相差甚远，一旦进行加载将可能导致加载失败或 MOD 无法运作的情况。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/save/LoadGameDialogOld$3.createImpl - String - "This save is using a mod version that's a minor mismatch from the one you have enabled. There is a possibility it may fail to load, or to work properly once loaded."
constant: This save is using a mod version that's a minor mismatch from the one you have enabled. There is a possibility it may fail to load, or to work properly once loaded.
constantCN: 该存档中的 MOD 版本与你启用的版本并不匹配，一旦进行加载将可能导致加载失败或 MOD 无法运作的情况。
点 额外经验 [来自之前花费的

constant: Whether this weapon is assigned to this group. Shift-click to assign all weapons of the same type.
constantCN: 是否将这个武器分配给本组。按住 Shift 键并点击，即可将所有同名武器分配给该组。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/wgd2/WeaponGroupDialogV2.<init> - String - "Flux per second generated by the sustained firing of this group. Some weapons are capable of higher burst fire - due to ammo, charges, and similar mechanics; this value does not reflect the resultant higher initial flux generation."
constant: Flux per second generated by the sustained firing of this group. Some weapons are capable of higher burst fire - due to ammo, charges, and similar mechanics; this value does not reflect the resultant higher initial flux generation.
constantCN: 一组武器持续开火时每秒产生的幅能。因有些武器具备更高的爆发力，所以这一数值并不能反映前者开始所额外产生的幅能。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Welcome to the advanced combat tutorial. Let's get started!"
constant: Welcome to the advanced combat tutorial. Let's get started!
constantCN: 欢迎来到高级作战教程。让我们开始吧！

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Your flagship is still the same Hammerhead, but the point defense lasers have been swapped out for Ion Cannons - more on those later."
constant: Your flagship is still the same Hammerhead, but the point defense lasers have been swapped out for Ion Cannons - more on those later.
constantCN: 您的旗舰仍是艘 锤头-级，但 PD 激光替换成离子炮 - 这将在之后将会被详细说明。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "We've already gone over the basics of using weapons in the previous tutorial. Now, let's take a look at picking the right weapon for the job."
constant: We've already gone over the basics of using weapons in the previous tutorial. Now, let's take a look at picking the right weapon for the job.
constantCN: 前面我们差不多完成了基本的武器使用教程，现在，让我们看看该如何挑选合适的武器进行攻击。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Each weapon deals damage of a particular damage type. Kinetic damage deals 200% to shields, but only 50% to armor."
constant: Each weapon deals damage of a particular damage type.\n\nKinetic damage deals 200% to shields, but only 50% to armor.
constantCN: 每一种武器都会拥有一种特定的伤害类型。\n\n动能伤害 能对护盾造成 200% 的伤害，但对装甲却只能造成 50% 的伤害。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Since the enemy ship has its shields up, let's start off by firing some Sabot missiles at it - they are extremely effective at bringing down shields."
constant: Since the enemy ship has its shields up, let's start off by firing some Sabot missiles at it - they are extremely effective at bringing down shields.
constantCN: 因敌舰开启了护盾，所以发射些赛博 SRM 导弹 - 它们对护盾非常有效。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Fire enough Sabots at the enemy ship to overload its shields."
constant: Fire enough Sabots at the enemy ship to overload its shields.
constantCN: 按 2 键切换武器并发射足够数量的赛博 SRM 使敌舰的护盾过载。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Great work! With the shields down and an overload in progress, the enemy ship is vulnerable. The next step is to bring down its armor."
constant: Great work! With the shields down and an overload in progress, the enemy ship is vulnerable. The next step is to bring down its armor.
constantCN: 真棒！当敌舰过载时护盾会关闭，并暴露弱点，下一步我们将摧毁它的装甲。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "High explosive damage deals 200% to armor, but only 50% to shields."
constant: High explosive damage deals 200% to armor, but only 50% to shields.
constantCN: 高爆伤害 能对装甲造成 200% 的伤害，但对护盾却只能造成 50% 的伤害。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Switch to your Assault Chainguns and punch through the armor. To break through faster, focus your fire on one spot."
constant: Switch to your Assault Chainguns and punch through the armor. To break through faster, focus your fire on one spot.
constantCN: 切换至 突击链炮 来打穿装甲，为了能更快地打破装甲，请将火力集中在一点之上。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Excellent, the enemy ship is taking hull damage now. Let's finish it off!"
constant: Excellent, the enemy ship is taking hull damage now. Let's finish it off!
constantCN: 非常好，现在敌舰的结构正受到伤害。让我们来了结它吧！

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Use the Accelerated Ammo Feeder to deal damage faster. Press %s to activate it, and fire away. If your flux maxes out from firing, just wait a bit so it can dissipate."
constant: Use the Accelerated Ammo Feeder to deal damage faster. Press %s to activate it, and fire away.\n\nIf your flux maxes out from firing, just wait a bit so it can dissipate.
constantCN: 使用 加速填弹器 更快地造成伤害。按 %s 将其激活，并持续开火。\n\n如果您的幅能因开火而接近幅能上限，只需稍作等待即可让其自然耗散。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Be careful - when a ship is disabled, the explosion deals damage to all nearby ships, except for fighters."
constant: Be careful - when a ship is disabled, the explosion deals damage to all nearby ships, except for fighters.
constantCN: 小心 - 当舰船停机，爆炸将对附近所有的舰船造成伤害，战机不受爆炸影响。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Make sure you're far enough away to avoid damage. About a ship's length should be enough."
constant: Make sure you're far enough away to avoid damage. About a ship's length should be enough.
constantCN: 确定您离得足够远来规避伤害，大概保持空出一艘船的距离。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Good work. There are two damage types we haven't looked at yet."
constant: Good work.\n\nThere are two damage types we haven't looked at yet.
constantCN: 干得不错。\n\n除此之外，我们还有两种伤害类型尚未展示。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Fragmentation damage deals only 25% to armor and shields, but usually costs little flux and has a high base DPS value, making it effective vs exposed hull, or lightly armored, unshielded targets - like missiles and fighters."
constant: Fragmentation damage deals only 25% to armor and shields, but usually costs little flux and has a high base DPS value, making it effective vs exposed hull, or lightly armored, unshielded targets - like missiles and fighters.
constantCN: 破片伤害 只对装甲和护盾造成 25% 的伤害，但幅能产出很少且基础伤害很高，因此能有效对抗没有装甲保护的结构、轻型装甲，没有护盾的目标 - 如导弹和战机。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Energy damage deals 100% of its listed damage to everything."
constant: Energy damage deals 100% of its listed damage to everything.
constantCN: 能量伤害 能对任何目标造成 100% 的伤害。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Some weapons also deal EMP damage in addition to their normal damage type."
constant: Some weapons also deal EMP damage in addition to their normal damage type.
constantCN: 而一些武器也同样会在它们的基础伤害之外造成额外的 EMP 效果。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "EMP damage does not affect shields, armor, or hull - but it can quickly disable enemy weapons and engines."
constant: EMP damage does not affect shields, armor, or hull - but it can quickly disable enemy weapons and engines.
constantCN: EMP 效果不会对护盾、装甲、结构造成直接伤害 - 但它能迅速瘫痪敌舰武器和引擎。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Your Ion Cannons deal lots of EMP damage (and little else). Switch to the Ion Cannons and disable some of the weapons on the Enforcer."
constant: Your Ion Cannons deal lots of EMP damage (and little else). Switch to the Ion Cannons and disable some of the weapons on the Enforcer.
constantCN: 您的离子炮可以造成大量的 EMP 效果 (和一点点其他的伤害) 切换到离子炮攻击 执法者-级 来瘫痪它的武器。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Excellent. Now, maneuver behind the enemy ship to disable its engines. You'll need to take out more than half to cause a total flameout."
constant: Excellent. Now, maneuver behind the enemy ship to disable its engines. You'll need to take out more than half to cause a total flameout.
constantCN: 很好！现在移动至其后方去瘫痪它的引擎。您需瘫痪一半以上的引擎来导致其熄火。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "That ship is now a sitting duck - it won't be able to maneuver at all until the engines are back online."
constant: That ship is now a sitting duck - it won't be able to maneuver at all until the engines are back online.
constantCN: 敌舰现在无法动弹了 - 它将无法移动，直到它的引擎重新恢复工作。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Non-EMP weapons can also disable engines and weapons, but EMP weapons bypass armor and get the job done faster."
constant: Non-EMP weapons can also disable engines and weapons, but EMP weapons bypass armor and get the job done faster.
constantCN: 不具备 EMP 效果的武器也能使引擎和武器失效，但 EMP 能绕过装甲更快完成任务。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Let's take another look at shields. Turn on your shields and sit tight for a moment - you'll be attacked with beam weapons."
constant: Let's take another look at shields. Turn on your shields and sit tight for a moment - you'll be attacked with beam weapons.
constantCN: 让我们看看另一种情况，现在打开护盾稍等片刻 - 您将受到光束武器的攻击。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "As you can see, your ship is not building up flux despite the shields being under fire."
constant: As you can see, your ship is not building up flux despite the shields being under fire.
constantCN: 如您所见，火力作用于护盾上却没有造成幅能上涨。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "This is because beam weapons generate soft flux when hitting shields."
constant: This is because beam weapons generate soft flux when hitting shields.
constantCN: 这是因为光束武器只会对护盾输出软幅能。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "This may make them seem weak - but remember that this flux still needs to be dissipated, leaving that much less flux dissipation to power weapons. Beam weapons are also very efficient and need little flux to fire."
constant: This may make them seem weak - but remember that this flux still needs to be dissipated, leaving that much less flux dissipation to power weapons. Beam weapons are also very efficient and need little flux to fire.
constantCN: 尽管这让它们看起来不怎么强大 - 但要记得软幅能也是需要耗散的，因此从某种意义上来说，这会间接削弱开盾时幅能耗散的速率，所以只产生少量幅能的光束武器仍然十分高效。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Ships receive an engine boost - a bonus to top speed and maneuverability - when their flux level and flux generation are at zero."
constant: Ships receive an engine boost - a bonus to top speed and maneuverability - when their flux level and flux generation are at zero.
constantCN: 当舰船幅能水平保持为零，且不产出任何幅能时，将受到 零幅能加速 的增益 - 这影响最高航速与机动性。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Turning shields on - even without taking any damage - is enough to cancel the bonus."
constant: Turning shields on - even without taking any damage - is enough to cancel the bonus.
constantCN: 要注意，当打开护盾时 - 即便没受到任何伤害 - 其产生的幅能也足以取消加成。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Travel through the nebula in front of your ship, noting how your ship moves faster when the shields are down."
constant: Travel through the nebula in front of your ship, noting how your ship moves faster when the shields are down.
constantCN: 让您的舰船穿过您面前的星云，请关注关闭护盾时您的舰船移动地更快。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "The engine boost is particularly important for larger ships, which have a much lower top speed without it."
constant: The engine boost is particularly important for larger ships, which have a much lower top speed without it.
constantCN: 该增益对大型舰船尤为重要，因为在没有加成的时候其航行速度往往极为缓慢。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "To maintain the engine boost for a ship with autofiring weapons, you can press %s to hold fire. Carriers will also need to press %s to pull back their fighters."
constant: To maintain the engine boost for a ship with autofiring weapons, you can press %s to hold fire.\n\nCarriers will also need to press %s to pull back their fighters.
constantCN: 为了让一艘开启了自动开火的舰船维持 零幅能加速 增益，您可以按 %s 全舰停火。\n\n航母则还需要按 %s 让其战机回归到整备状态。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/OoOO.createScript - String - "Congratulations! You've completed the advanced combat tutorial. It's probably a good idea to complete the fleet command tutorial next."
constant: Congratulations! You've completed the advanced combat tutorial.\n\nIt's probably a good idea to complete the fleet command tutorial next.
constantCN: 恭喜！您已经完成了高级战斗教程。\n\n接下来完成舰队指挥教程将是个好主意。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/Objectsuper$3.createImpl - String - "The strength of the ground defenses affects the effectiveness of raids and other ground operations against the colony. It also increases the amount of fuel required to bombard it."
constant: The strength of the ground defenses affects the effectiveness of raids and other ground operations against the colony. It also increases the amount of fuel required to bombard it.
constantCN: 地面防御战力的强弱将影响对殖民地突袭和其他对地行动的效果。并且它还会增加轰炸殖民地时所需的燃料量。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/Objectsuper$1.createImpl - String - "The colony's stability is a measure of the strength of the local government and its ability to effectively muster and leverage the resources of the colony."
constant: The colony's stability is a measure of the strength of the local government and its ability to effectively muster and leverage the resources of the colony.
constantCN: 市场的稳定性是衡量地方政府的整体实力和繁荣的标准。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/Objectsuper$1.createImpl - String - "A more stable colony produces larger fleets with well-maintained ships."
constant: A more stable colony produces larger fleets with well-maintained ships.
constantCN: 一处高稳定的殖民地会拥有更多维护良好的舰船以及更大的舰队。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/Objectsuper$1.createImpl - String - "A stable colony is also more resistant to raids and invasions, and has less black market activity."
constant: A stable colony is also more resistant to raids and invasions, and has less black market activity.
constantCN: 一处高稳定的殖民地不仅能有效抵御袭击与入侵，且黑市活动 也将遭到遏制。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/Objectsuper$1.createImpl - String - "A colony that's unstable for too long runs the risk of becoming decivilized."
constant: A colony that's unstable for too long runs the risk of becoming decivilized.
constantCN: 一处长期处于不稳定的殖民地将更容易遭受不可预见的危险，直至文明毁灭。
舰队规模 & 舰船质量

constant: Laying in an intercept course for

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/CampaignState.showShuttleDialog - String - "Your fleet is scattered, and you yourself barely escape in the command pod. After a while, you're picked up by a passing salvage fleet and taken back to civilization. Eventually, you acquire another couple of craft and are able to ply the space lanes once again."
constant: Your fleet is scattered, and you yourself barely escape in the command pod.\n\nAfter a while, you're picked up by a passing salvage fleet and taken back to civilization. Eventually, you acquire another couple of craft and are able to ply the space lanes once again.
constantCN: 你的舰队四散溃逃，而你本人则乘坐指挥舱勉强逃生。\n\n一段时间以后，你被一支路过的打捞舰队救起，并被带回文明社会。最终，你又获得了几艘飞船，得以重返太空航道。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/CampaignState.showShuttleDialog - String - "Some automated ships in your fleet still remain operational, but they're unable to find your command pod. RAW: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/ui/marketinfo/GroundRaidTargetPickerDialog.addTooltips - String - "Danger level your marines will face to achieve this objective. Higher danger level increases casualties. Certain commodities and items are inherently more dangerous to acquire. A commodity shortage makes an operation more dangerous, while excess stockpiles are more easily accessible and decrease the risks faced by your marines. In addition, a commodity that's locally produced - rather than imported - is less dangerous to acquire. Casualties are also affected by other factors; hover over the "Projected marine casualties" for details."
constant:
Danger level your marines will face to achieve this objective. Higher danger level increases casualties.

Certain commodities and items are inherently more dangerous to acquire.

A commodity shortage makes an operation more dangerous, while excess stockpiles are more easily accessible and decrease the risks faced by your marines. In addition, a commodity that's locally produced - rather than imported - is less dangerous to acquire.

Casualties are also affected by other factors; hover over the "Projected marine casualties" for details.
constantCN:
达成所选目标的危险程度，危险程度越高，伤亡也越高。

某些商品或物品的相关危险程度将尤其地高。

对短缺的商品执行行动往往更加危险，而多余的库存往往更容易获得，且陆战队员面临的风险也将更小。此外，本地生产的商品 (而不是进口的) 的获取危险性也相对较小。

其他因素也会影响伤亡人数，将鼠标指针悬停在 "预计伤亡人数" 一栏以查看详情。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/combat/OOoO.?00000 - String - "You may have noticed that using weapons and absorbing damage with shields builds up flux. When flux reaches maximum, you risk overload and can't fire your weapons, but if you wait, it will slowly dissipate. There's a faster way - press V to vent all flux from the ship. You won't be able to fire or use shields while it's venting, but it's much faster than waiting for it to dissipate naturally. Press V after dismissing this dialog to see how it works."
constant:
You may have noticed that using weapons and absorbing damage with shields builds up flux.

When flux reaches maximum, you risk overload and can't fire your weapons, but if you wait, it will slowly dissipate.

There's a faster way - press V to vent all flux from the ship. You won't be able to fire or use shields while it's venting, but it's much faster than waiting for it to dissipate naturally.

Press V after dismissing this dialog to see how it works.
constantCN:
您可能注意到，武器开火与护盾吸收伤害将提高 幅能。

当幅能抵达上限，您将 过载 并无法开火，而此时您只能稍作等待，让幅能缓慢耗散。

还有更快的耗散方式 - 按 V 强制排散 舰船的所有幅能。排散幅能时，您将无法开火或使用护盾，但其幅能耗散速率将远高于自然耗散。

在关闭此对话框后按 V 并观察它的运作。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/combat/OOoO.String - String - "Press V to vent flux from your ship."
constant: Press V to vent flux from your ship.
constantCN: 按 V 键让你的舰船排放幅能。

Welcome to the fleet command tutorial.

At the start of a battle, you will want to deploy some of your ships. To do so, click on ship icons to mark them for deployment and then press the "Deploy" button.

Deploying ships requires fleet points. Right now, you only have a few points, so go ahead and <
highlight>
deploy just the Wasp interceptor wing after dismissing this dialog.<
/highlight>
constantCN:
欢迎来到舰队指挥教程。

在战斗开始时，您将希望部署您的部分舰船。为了部署舰船，点击标志着舰船的图标以选中舰船，然后按 "部署" 按钮。

部署舰船需要部署点。就目前而言，您只有少量部署点，所以先<highlight>在关闭此对话框后仅部署黄蜂拦截机。</highlight>

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/oOOO/F.super - String - "You can press %s to open and close the map, and %s to pause and unpause. To pan your view, right-click on an empty spot on the map and drag. constant:
You can press %s to open and close the map, and %s to pause and unpause. To pan your view, right-click on an empty spot on the map and drag.

You can also see what your ships are doing by clicking on them and then selecting "Show Video Feed" from the context menu.

<
highlight>
With the map open, select your interceptor wing and click "Show Video Feed" to follow along as it captures the Comm Relay.<
/highlight>
constantCN:
您可以按 %s 关闭或打开地图，并按 %s 暂停游戏或解除暂停。如需调整您的视野，在地图上按住右键并拖动鼠标。

您也可以点击您的舰船并在命令列表中选择 "接通视频信号" 观察它们的行为。

<highlight>打开地图，选择您的拦截机，并点击 "接通视频信号" 观察它们占领通讯中继站。</highlight>

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/oOOO/F.?00000 - String - "Good! Good! You'll need additional fleet points to deploy the rest of your fleet, and you can get them by capturing objectives.

<

constantCN:
很好！您需要更多部署点来部署您舰队的剩余舰船，您可以通过占领目标获取部署点。

指派命令需要消耗一个指挥点，如果您的指挥点耗尽，那么您就无法下令。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/oOOO/C.super - String - "Let's set up to give it a warm welcome. <

 The Dagger torpedo bombers, being the only strike craft in your fleet, will go there.
constantCN: 让我们准备给它来个热烈欢迎。首先，在地图中上方集结一队打击力量 - 传感器阵列左边一两个地图格的位置应该不错。\n\n<highlight>在目标位置按左键来创造一个路径点，并在命令列表中选择 "联队突击集结点"。</highlight>匕首鱼雷轰炸机，这是您舰队中的唯一轰炸机，将前往此处。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/oOOO/C.super - String - "Good, the bombers are on their way. In the meantime, the interceptors have decided to attack the cruiser on their own, and the Gemini is moving up to do so as well. We don't want that - the Gemini is a freighter/carrier, and no match for a cruiser in direct combat, and neither are the interceptors. <highlight>Left click behind your lines to make another waypoint, and select "Rally Carrier Group" to keep the Gemini there and out of trouble.</highlight>"
constant:
Good, the bombers are on their way.

In the meantime, the interceptors have decided to attack the cruiser on their own, and the Gemini is moving up to do so as well. We don't want that - the Gemini is a freighter/carrier, and no match for a cruiser in direct combat, and neither are the interceptors.

<
highlight>
Left click behind your lines to make another waypoint, and select "Rally Carrier Group" to keep the Gemini there and out of trouble.<
/highlight>
constantCN:
很好，轰炸机正在它们的航线上了。

与此同时，拦截机自行决定攻击这艘巡洋舰，而 双子座-级 也向上移动展开攻击。我们不希望那样 - 双子座-级 是一艘武装货船航母，无法正面对抗一艘战斗巡洋舰，且拦截机也做不到这一点。

<highlight>左键点击你的战巡后方创造一个路径点，然后选择 "航母集结点" 让 双子座-级 留在该处避免冲突。</highlight>

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/oOOO/C.?00000 - String - "Great work. Notice how the sensor array lifts the fog of war in a large radius - and it turns out there's an enemy cruiser lurking nearby! Let's take a closer look."

constantCN: 干得不错。注意到传感器清空了一大片阵列战争迷雾 - 并发现了一艘潜伏在附近的敌方巡洋舰！\n\n让我们凑近些看看。

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/combat/ooOO.?00000 - String - "Excellent! Time for some live-fire training exercises. This next frigate will fight back - use what you've learned to defeat it. constant:
Excellent! Time for some live-fire training exercises.

This next frigate will fight back - use what you've learned to defeat it. Its engines are crippled, so don't worry about it running away.

constantCN:
干得漂亮！该拿真家伙试试手了。

按 鼠标右键 开启或关闭你的护盾 - 您会用得上它的！

RAW: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/oOOO/B.super - String - "Smart work, the enemy cruiser is disabled! 匕首鱼雷轰炸机的弹药已耗尽，它们会回到其母舰 (即 双子座-级) 补充弹药。地图上的蓝色箭头显示了它们的方向。

在整备完成后，这些轰炸机将全副武装地重新起飞 - 让一艘航母就近支援可以让您的战机发挥最大的作用。
